---
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<header class="home-intro">
		<h1>Hello there.</h1>
		<div class="home-copy">
			<p>
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer vitae
				metus a justo varius aliquet. Donec at neque sed erat malesuada
				fermentum, sit amet commodo nisl.
			</p>
			<p>
				Praesent vel sem non ligula posuere consequat. Suspendisse potenti.
				Curabitur finibus, lacus quis consequat volutpat, sapien nibh tempor
				erat, vitae interdum ipsum neque vel lorem.
			</p>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="home-visuals" aria-label="A few things">
		<figure class="home-figure home-figure--wide">
			<picture>
				<source
					type="image/avif"
					srcset="/images/home/water-900.avif 900w, /images/home/water.avif 1800w"
					sizes="(max-width: 640px) calc(100vw - 2rem), 56rem"
				/>
				<source
					type="image/webp"
					srcset="/images/home/water-900.webp 900w, /images/home/water.webp 1800w"
					sizes="(max-width: 640px) calc(100vw - 2rem), 56rem"
				/>
				<img
					src="/images/home/water.webp"
					alt="Black-and-white close-up of rippling water."
					width="1800"
					height="900"
					decoding="async"
				/>
			</picture>
			<figcaption>
				<span>Deep lake, 2025</span>
				<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/abstract-black-and-white-waves-with-light-reflections-YVQCoZbtUrA">Linus Belanger</a>
			</figcaption>
		</figure>

		<div class="home-feature-row">
			<div class="home-copy home-copy--side">
				<p>
					Aliquam erat volutpat. Morbi euismod augue vitae lectus viverra, quis
					fringilla libero ultricies. Sed pretium enim id urna tincidunt, vitae
					mollis tortor malesuada.
				</p>
				<p>
					Maecenas consequat, risus a dignissim tincidunt, arcu odio feugiat
					mauris, sit amet sodales velit justo vel nibh. Nulla facilisi. Vivamus
					convallis sem nec augue faucibus, at luctus erat pulvinar.
				</p>
				<p>
					Fusce aliquam quam non justo malesuada, nec feugiat lacus hendrerit.
					Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada
					fames ac turpis egestas.
				</p>
			</div>

			<figure class="home-figure">
				<picture>
					<source
						type="image/avif"
						srcset="/images/home/architecture-550.avif 550w, /images/home/architecture.avif 1100w"
						sizes="(max-width: 640px) calc(100vw - 2rem), 24rem"
					/>
					<source
						type="image/webp"
						srcset="/images/home/architecture-550.webp 550w, /images/home/architecture.webp 1100w"
						sizes="(max-width: 640px) calc(100vw - 2rem), 24rem"
					/>
					<img
						src="/images/home/architecture.webp"
						alt="Low-angle black-and-white view of a geometric modern building."
						width="1100"
						height="1467"
						loading="lazy"
						decoding="async"
					/>
				</picture>
				<figcaption>
					<span>Tokyo, 2025</span>
					<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/modern-architecture-with-geometric-lines-and-shadows-yRs7byyVBFc">Sebastian Schuster</a>
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</div>

		<figure class="home-figure home-figure--closing">
			<picture>
				<source
					type="image/avif"
					srcset="/images/home/street-tree-wide-900.avif 900w, /images/home/street-tree-wide.avif 1800w"
					sizes="(max-width: 640px) calc(100vw - 2rem), 56rem"
				/>
				<source
					type="image/webp"
					srcset="/images/home/street-tree-wide-900.webp 900w, /images/home/street-tree-wide.webp 1800w"
					sizes="(max-width: 640px) calc(100vw - 2rem), 56rem"
				/>
				<img
					src="/images/home/street-tree-wide.webp"
					alt="Black-and-white branches crossing a tiled city building."
					width="1800"
					height="1080"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
				/>
			</picture>
			<figcaption>
				<span>Street study, 2023</span>
				<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/a-black-and-white-photo-of-a-tree-in-front-of-a-building-qbTkG1tqmvo">Mak</a>
			</figcaption>
		</figure>
	</section>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	.home-intro {
		padding-top: clamp(0.5rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(3.25rem, 10vw, 5.75rem);
		font-weight: 610;
		letter-spacing: -0.065em;
		line-height: 0.95;
	}

	.home-copy {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--muted-foreground);
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.08rem);
		line-height: 1.75;
	}

	.home-copy p {
		margin: 0 0 1.35rem;
	}

	.home-copy p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.home-visuals {
		margin-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4rem);
	}

	.home-figure {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.home-figure picture,
	.home-figure img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.home-figure img {
		height: auto;
		background: var(--muted);
	}

	.home-figure figcaption {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-top: 0.65rem;
		color: var(--muted-foreground);
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}

	.home-figure figcaption a {
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
		text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
	}

	.home-figure figcaption a:hover,
	.home-figure figcaption a:focus-visible {
		color: var(--foreground);
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.home-feature-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 11fr) minmax(0, 9fr);
		gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
		align-items: start;
		margin-top: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
	}

	.home-copy--side {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.home-figure--closing {
		margin-top: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
	}

	@media (max-width: 560px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 17vw, 4.6rem);
		}

		.home-feature-row {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2.5rem;
			margin-top: 3rem;
		}

		.home-figure--closing {
			margin-top: 3.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
